3rd ed. New York: Norton, 2002.</p>

<p><strong>Berlioz, Hector</strong>  <br />
<em>Treatise on Instrumentation</em>  <br />
Enl. and rev. Richard Strauss. Tran. Theodore Front. New York: Dover, 1991.</p>

<p><strong>Blatter, Alfred</strong>   <br />
<em>Instrumentation and Orchestration</em>   <br />
2nd ed. New York, Schirmer Books, 1997.</p>

<p><strong>Forsyth, Cecil</strong>  <br />
<em>Orchestration</em>  <br />
2nd ed. New York: Dover, 1982.</p>

