<em>Orchestral Technique</em><br />
3rd. ed. London and New York: Oxford University Press, 1982.</p>

<p><strong>Kennan, Kent</strong> and <strong>Grantham, Donald</strong><br />
<em>Technique of Orchestration</em><br />
6th ed. New Jersey: Prentice Hall, 2002.</p>

